==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oilnut
<hw>Oil"nut`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
buffalo nut. See <cref>Buffalo nut</cref>, under
<er>Buffalo</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name is also applied to various nuts and seeds
yielding oil, as the butternut, cocoanut, oil-palm nut.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>oil patch</ent>⟦br⟧
